        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、VMware虚拟机安装"><a href="#一、VMware虚拟机安装" class="headerlink" title="一、VMware虚拟机安装"></a>一、VMware虚拟机安装</h2><h3 id="1-下载VMware17-5"><a href="#1-下载VMware17-5" class="headerlink" title="1.下载VMware17.5"></a>1.下载VMware17.5</h3><ul><li>下载地址：<a href="https://download3.vmware.com/software/WKST-1750-WIN/VMware-workstation-full-17.5.0-22583795.exe">https://download3.vmware.com/software/WKST-1750-WIN/VMware-workstation-full-17.5.0-22583795.exe</a></li></ul><h3 id="2-安装VMware17-5"><a href="#2-安装VMware17-5" class="headerlink" title="2.安装VMware17.5"></a>2.安装VMware17.5</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312030471.png" alt="image-20240131203008388"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312034340.png" alt="image-20240131203422261"></p><p>不要更改安装位置，全部单击”下一步”，输入注册码请从“激活码”激活即可。</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312036099.png" alt="image-20240131203647049"></p><h2 id="二、Ubuntu安装"><a href="#二、Ubuntu安装" class="headerlink" title="二、Ubuntu安装"></a>二、Ubuntu安装</h2><h3 id="1-下载Ubuntu16-4"><a href="#1-下载Ubuntu16-4" class="headerlink" title="1.下载Ubuntu16.4"></a>1.下载Ubuntu16.4</h3><p>链接：<a href="https://share.weiyun.com/6wwSC0rz">https://share.weiyun.com/6wwSC0rz</a> 密码：e8jy64</p><h3 id="2-安装Ubuntu16-4"><a href="#2-安装Ubuntu16-4" class="headerlink" title="2.安装Ubuntu16.4"></a>2.安装Ubuntu16.4</h3><h4 id="创建虚拟机及载入镜像"><a href="#创建虚拟机及载入镜像" class="headerlink" title="创建虚拟机及载入镜像"></a>创建虚拟机及载入镜像</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312048675.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h4 id="Ubuntu安装"><a href="#Ubuntu安装" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu安装"></a>Ubuntu安装</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312053185.png" alt="image-20240131205336122"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312105555.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><p>重启</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312108161.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h2 id="三、安装VMware-tools"><a href="#三、安装VMware-tools" class="headerlink" title="三、安装VMware tools"></a>三、安装VMware tools</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312120717.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h2 id="四、samba服务器"><a href="#四、samba服务器" class="headerlink" title="四、samba服务器"></a>四、samba服务器</h2><h3 id="1-安装samba服务器"><a href="#1-安装samba服务器" class="headerlink" title="1.安装samba服务器"></a>1.安装samba服务器</h3><h4 id="更新安装源："><a href="#更新安装源：" class="headerlink" title="更新安装源："></a>更新安装源：</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312136941.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h4 id="安装samba的核心插件"><a href="#安装samba的核心插件" class="headerlink" title="安装samba的核心插件"></a>安装samba的核心插件</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install samba</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312138040.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h4 id="修改-etc-samba下的配置文件smb-conf"><a href="#修改-etc-samba下的配置文件smb-conf" class="headerlink" title="修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba下的配置文件smb.conf"></a>修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba下的配置文件smb.conf</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo gedit /etc/samba/smb.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312139376.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h4 id="在该文件smb-conf的最末尾添加↓"><a href="#在该文件smb-conf的最末尾添加↓" class="headerlink" title="在该文件smb.conf的最末尾添加↓"></a>在该文件smb.conf的最末尾添加↓</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[han1993]</span><br><span class="line">    comment = samba home directory </span><br><span class="line">    path = /home/han1993</span><br><span class="line">    public = yes</span><br><span class="line">    browseable = yes</span><br><span class="line">    public = yes</span><br><span class="line">    read only = no</span><br><span class="line">    valid users = han1993</span><br><span class="line">    create mask = 0777</span><br><span class="line">    directory mask = 0777 </span><br><span class="line">    force user = han1993</span><br><span class="line">    force group = han1993</span><br><span class="line">    available = yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312140401.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h4 id="重启samba服务器"><a href="#重启samba服务器" class="headerlink" title="重启samba服务器"></a>重启samba服务器</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo /etc/init.d/samba restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo service smbd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312141544.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h3 id="2-配置服务器的用户名以及密码"><a href="#2-配置服务器的用户名以及密码" class="headerlink" title="2.配置服务器的用户名以及密码"></a>2.配置服务器的用户名以及密码</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo smbpasswd -a han1993</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>用户为当前登录的用户密码可以和Ubuntu系统密码不同</p><p>后面将提示输入samba的用户密码</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312145926.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h3 id="3-windows访问samba服务器"><a href="#3-windows访问samba服务器" class="headerlink" title="3.windows访问samba服务器"></a>3.windows访问samba服务器</h3><p>查看ubuntu的ip地址</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ifconfig</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312154430.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h2 id="五、shh服务器"><a href="#五、shh服务器" class="headerlink" title="五、shh服务器"></a>五、shh服务器</h2><p>windows用户可以通过  ssh服务器 远程控制ubuntu的终端 </p><h3 id="1-安装ssh服务器"><a href="#1-安装ssh服务器" class="headerlink" title="1.安装ssh服务器"></a>1.安装ssh服务器</h3><p>安装ssh服务器</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install openssh-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312203142.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><p>查看ssh是否安装运行：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ps -A | grep ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312205032.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h3 id="2-putty通过shh连接Ubuntu系统终端"><a href="#2-putty通过shh连接Ubuntu系统终端" class="headerlink" title="2.putty通过shh连接Ubuntu系统终端"></a>2.putty通过shh连接Ubuntu系统终端</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312208978.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p><h3 id="3-winscp通过ssh连接Ubuntu文件管理"><a href="#3-winscp通过ssh连接Ubuntu文件管理" class="headerlink" title="3.winscp通过ssh连接Ubuntu文件管理"></a>3.winscp通过ssh连接Ubuntu文件管理</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/cn-z/typroa-images/raw/master/images/202401312211865.gif" alt="虚拟机"></p>]]></content>
      
      
